Mark, uskoro ce svako
ovde znati ko si ti.

502
00:44:39,500 --> 00:44:41,500
-Je li tako?
-Da.

503
00:44:41,500 --> 00:44:44,500
Do Boga, ti si tako nevin.
Lepo to videti.

504
00:44:52,500 --> 00:44:53,500
Telo Hrista.

505
00:45:09,250 --> 00:45:10,250
Telo Hrista.

506
00:45:11,750 --> 00:45:12,750
Amen.

507
00:45:20,500 --> 00:45:21,500
Telo Hrista.

508
00:45:22,000 --> 00:45:23,000
Amen.

509
00:45:32,000 --> 00:45:33,000
Ovo je neverovatno!

510
00:45:33,750 --> 00:45:34,750
Moram da priznam.

511
00:45:34,750 --> 00:45:37,750
Dobro se uklapas, za jednog mladog decka
iz jednog malog grada u Ontariju.

512
00:45:39,000 --> 00:45:40,750
Ja, u mojim vremenima, nebi ovo uradijo.

513
00:45:40,750 --> 00:45:42,250
Nebi mogo, sta ti mozes.

514
00:45:42,250 --> 00:45:43,750
Da, Mark je svakad znao ko je.

515
00:45:43,750 --> 00:45:44,750
Pravnik?

516
00:45:45,500 --> 00:45:48,500
Hoces da trazimo na Kvin Strit
haljinu za matursko? Zbog prerade.

517
00:45:48,500 --> 00:45:49,500
Izvini, savrseno.

518
00:45:50,000 --> 00:45:51,500
-Stvarno?
-Ne panikuj.

519
00:45:51,500 --> 00:45:53,500
Ne, ti ces sigurno bit ponosan na mene.

520
00:45:53,500 --> 00:45:55,500
Ali, moraces da cekas do matuskog da je vidis.

521
00:45:55,500 --> 00:45:58,000
Mislim, izvini, ako idemo na matursko.

522
00:45:58,000 --> 00:45:59,000
Kazite mi da idemo.

523
00:45:59,000 --> 00:46:01,000
Radim sta mogu. Ne obecavam.

524
00:46:03,500 --> 00:46:05,500
Ono... ono je Otis.

525
00:46:07,250 --> 00:46:09,750
-Sta?
-Milosrdni Oce!

526
00:46:22,500 --> 00:46:25,000
On ne porizuje svoju
homoseksualnost,

527
00:46:25,000 --> 00:46:30,000
ali ocekiva od nas, da porizujemo
ko smo i u sta verujemo.

528
00:46:32,500 --> 00:46:34,000
Nepodnosljivo.

529
00:46:36,000 --> 00:46:37,000
Ja ne znam.

530
00:46:39,250 --> 00:46:40,500
Vremena se menjaju.

531
00:46:42,000 --> 00:46:43,000
Nazalost.

532
00:46:51,000 --> 00:46:52,500
Ako se crkva nada da prezivi,

533
00:46:55,000 --> 00:46:56,500
mrzim da kazem,

534
00:46:58,500 --> 00:47:01,000
maracemo se promeniti uz vremena.

535
00:47:03,500 --> 00:47:04,500
Ne, da ja to zelim!

536
00:47:09,750 --> 00:47:12,750
C druge strane, cemo na
kraju biti potpuno sami.

537
00:47:33,500 --> 00:47:34,500
Jesi li u redu?

538
00:47:38,500 --> 00:47:39,500
Jesi li ti u redu?

539
00:47:41,500 --> 00:47:42,500
Da.

540
00:47:47,000 --> 00:47:48,000
Hocu da kazem...

541
00:47:51,500 --> 00:47:53,500
Moj sin ce nositi aktovku.

542
00:48:13,500 --> 00:48:15,500
Hoce li biti "Kraljica Maturskog"?

543
00:48:22,750 --> 00:48:25,250
I ovo je, Gdini. i Gdice., sta ce
nasa dva princa nositi

544
00:48:25,500 --> 00:48:27,250
u ovo vreme sledece nedelje.

545
00:48:27,250 --> 00:48:28,250
Sad mozete da se presvucete.

546
00:48:29,000 --> 00:48:30,500
Mozemo li videti poljubac?

547
00:48:38,000 --> 00:48:40,000
To so moji momci.
Tako je fino.

548
00:48:46,500 --> 00:48:48,000
Onda... Ime je: Loni Vin.

549
00:48:49,000 --> 00:48:52,000
Pise se: V-I-N-N.
Dva "N"!

550
00:48:59,500 --> 00:49:01,000
Sta se desava tamo?

551
00:49:01,000 --> 00:49:02,750
Dosta!
Svega je dosta!

552
00:49:04,500 --> 00:49:06,000
Ne glumi sad "kraljicu drame".

553
00:49:06,000 --> 00:49:07,500
Sve ce biti u redu.

554
00:49:08,000 --> 00:49:09,000
Ne mogu.

555
00:49:14,000 --> 00:49:15,000
Sudenje je sledece nedelje.

556
00:49:15,000 --> 00:49:16,500
Ako pobedimo ili me, nije vazno.

557
00:49:20,500 --> 00:49:21,500
Halo?

558
00:49:25,000 --> 00:49:26,000
Halo!

559
00:49:30,500 --> 00:49:33,000
Haj. Ja...
Ja se izvinjavam.

560
00:49:43,000 --> 00:49:45,000
LJUTNJA U RAJU

561
00:49:56,500 --> 00:49:57,500
Izvinite!

562
00:49:58,000 --> 00:49:59,000
Pomerite se!

563
00:50:15,000 --> 00:50:16,000
Upozorenje, daci!

564
00:50:16,000 --> 00:50:22,000
U skoli nije dozvoljeno imati aktuelni broj
nepristojnog homoseksualnog magacina.

565
00:50:23,250 --> 00:50:24,250
Bez izuzetka!

566
00:50:24,750 --> 00:50:25,750
23cm!?

567
00:50:37,000 --> 00:50:38,000
Poludecemo.

568
00:50:38,000 --> 00:50:40,000
11.000 posetioca za 24 sata.

569
00:50:40,000 --> 00:50:42,000
Nema nista bole, nego lose glasine.

570
00:50:43,500 --> 00:50:45,000
Hej, momci. Slusajte.

571
00:50:45,000 --> 00:50:46,000
Oko maturskog...

572
00:50:47,000 --> 00:50:48,500
Imam neke teskoce.

573
00:50:49,500 --> 00:50:52,500
Devojke, sa kojima vi hocete da idete,
vec imaju partnera za bal.

574
00:50:52,500 --> 00:50:54,000
Morate ici sa nekim van skole.

575
00:50:55,000 --> 00:50:56,000
Je li to u redu?

576
00:50:58,250 --> 00:50:59,250
Sveze meso.

577
00:51:00,500 --> 00:51:01,500
Sveze meso.

578
00:51:01,500 --> 00:51:02,500
Tacno.

579
00:51:37,000 --> 00:51:38,000
Spreman?

580
00:51:39,500 --> 00:51:40,500
Nisam.

581
00:51:41,500 --> 00:51:42,500
Ona ti veruje.

582
00:51:42,500 --> 00:51:43,500
Voli te!

583
00:51:44,000 --> 00:51:46,000
Tebe je predlozila za stipendium.

584
00:51:47,250 --> 00:51:48,750
Ja mogu ici tamo sam.

585
00:51:48,750 --> 00:51:50,250
Veruj mi, postici ces.

586
00:51:50,250 --> 00:51:53,250
Ali, vazno je, da sud cuje
sta ona ima da kaze.

587
00:51:53,250 --> 00:51:54,250
Onda...

588
00:51:54,250 --> 00:51:57,250
Kad ti budes tamo, i to ces biti,

589
00:51:57,250 --> 00:52:00,750
sud ce razumet, da si naucijo
da mislis, da nije nikakva greska

590
00:52:00,750 --> 00:52:01,750
biti peder.

591
00:52:01,750 --> 00:52:03,750
Samo necu da je uvucem u teskoce.

592
00:52:03,750 --> 00:52:05,750
Ovo nije takmicenje omiljenosti.

593
00:52:06,000 --> 00:52:10,000
Gda. Lorenc je tebe naucila jednu
liberalnu katolicku perspektivu.

594
00:52:10,250 --> 00:52:13,250
Ucitelji salju protivrecne poruke.

595
00:52:13,250 --> 00:52:15,250
Oni nisu jedna spojena front.

596
00:52:17,000 --> 00:52:18,000
Ona je katolikinja.

597
00:52:18,000 --> 00:52:20,000
Ona zna da si peder.

598
00:52:20,000 --> 00:52:21,000
Ona je to prihvatila.

599
00:52:21,000 --> 00:52:24,000
I sad, katolicke podglavice
hoce tebe da kaznu za to?

600
00:52:24,750 --> 00:52:25,750
To je nomoguce.

601
00:52:29,250 --> 00:52:30,250
Da.

602
00:52:30,500 --> 00:52:34,250
Crkvena nauka je uvek otvorena
prema novim interpertacijama.

603
00:52:34,250 --> 00:52:35,750
Svakad je bilo tako.

604
00:52:37,500 --> 00:52:40,000
Sud to mora da shvati.
Tacka!

605
00:52:42,500 --> 00:52:44,000
-Okej.
-Tako je dobro.

606
00:52:44,000 --> 00:52:45,000
Zaslusavanje je sutra.

607
00:52:45,500 --> 00:52:46,500
Ugrabi je.

608
00:52:48,000 --> 00:52:49,000
Znas sta mislim.

609
00:53:11,000 --> 00:53:12,000
I?

610
00:53:12,000 --> 00:53:13,000
Uradice.

611
00:53:13,500 --> 00:53:14,500
Ti si moja "Kraljica Maturskog"!

612
00:53:19,500 --> 00:53:20,500
Upozorenje, daci!

613
00:53:21,000 --> 00:53:23,500
Skolski odevni red so mora postovati.

614
00:53:23,500 --> 00:53:27,500
Suknje ne smeju biti krace nego
malo iznad kolena, ne vise.

615
00:53:28,500 --> 00:53:29,500
Bez izuzetka!

616
00:53:42,000 --> 00:53:45,000
-Morao sam da te vidim.
-Nemozes biti ovde.

617
00:53:45,000 --> 00:53:46,500
Nisam cuo nista od tebe.

618
00:53:46,500 --> 00:53:49,000
Nije nista licno.
Nemogu ovo da uradim.

619
00:53:49,000 --> 00:53:50,000
Nikad nemozes.

620
00:53:51,000 --> 00:53:53,000
Ja nisam bijo "out", do sad.

621
00:53:53,750 --> 00:53:54,750
Znam.

622
00:53:55,500 --> 00:53:58,500
A sad... novinari, televizija
i sve to sranje.

623
00:54:00,000 --> 00:54:02,000
Ja se brinem o vebe... o nama.

624
00:54:02,000 --> 00:54:04,000
Nas? Vec davno nema "nas".

625
00:54:05,000 --> 00:54:06,500
Samo se brines o sebi.

626
00:54:06,500 --> 00:54:08,500
To uopste nije fer.

627
00:54:08,500 --> 00:54:09,500
Ti, ti, ti!

628
00:54:10,250 --> 00:54:11,250
Mark Hal?

629
00:54:14,000 --> 00:54:15,000
Da.

630
00:54:15,750 --> 00:54:17,000
Mogu li dobit autogram?

631
00:54:19,500 --> 00:54:20,500
Sigurno.

632
00:54:21,500 --> 00:54:22,500
Kako se zoves?

633
00:54:23,000 --> 00:54:24,000
Nik.

634
00:54:29,000 --> 00:54:30,000
Hvala.

635
00:54:30,500 --> 00:54:31,500
Izvinite.

636
00:54:32,750 --> 00:54:34,750
Imate li radio-sateve?

637
00:54:41,750 --> 00:54:42,750
Da.

638
00:54:51,000 --> 00:54:55,000
KANONSKO PRAVO
(Crkveno pravo)

639
00:55:51,500 --> 00:55:54,500
Katolicka crkva ce danas braniti
svoje pravo, da vodi svoje skole

640
00:55:54,500 --> 00:55:57,500
jednakovredno po vernim
vrednostima.

641
00:56:03,000 --> 00:56:04,000
Mark Hal.

642
00:56:04,500 --> 00:56:08,500
Bori se, za priznavanje svoje osobe, protiv
neprijateljski nastrojenog i nepopustljivog patriarhata.

643
00:56:09,000 --> 00:56:11,500
Hoce li ovaj postmoderni "Pepeljug"
moci da ide na svoj bal?

644
00:56:11,500 --> 00:56:12,500
Na vreme?

645
00:56:13,250 --> 00:56:14,250
Danas je zaslusavanje.

646
00:56:15,000 --> 00:56:17,500
Skolska uprava je uvredila ljudska
prava od Ontarija,

647
00:56:17,500 --> 00:56:21,000
skolsko zakonodavanje i
red uprave ove provincije,

648
00:56:21,000 --> 00:56:24,500
koji zabranjuju diskriminaciju
zbog seksualne orijentacije.

649
00:56:24,500 --> 00:56:26,500
Mark, cega se nadate da postignete?

650
00:56:27,750 --> 00:56:29,250
Samo hocu da idem na bal.

651
00:56:29,250 --> 00:56:31,250
Mark, gde je Dzejsen?
Gde je Vas momak?

652
00:56:33,000 --> 00:56:35,000
Izvinite, kasnimo.
Hvala.

653
00:56:38,000 --> 00:56:39,000
Ulazite.

654
00:56:39,500 --> 00:56:41,500
Izvinite. Medije su zabranjene.

655
00:56:43,500 --> 00:56:45,500
Za skolsku dokumentaciju filmujem.

656
00:56:45,500 --> 00:56:47,500
Nemozes uci.
Idi tamo.

657
00:56:56,000 --> 00:56:59,000
Podnosijoc sahteva trazi
dozvolu da ide na maturski

658
00:56:59,000 --> 00:57:02,000
bal sa partnerom svojeg izbora.

659
00:57:02,000 --> 00:57:03,000
Hocemo da nastavimo?

660
00:57:04,500 --> 00:57:05,500
Hocete nesto?

661
00:57:09,500 --> 00:57:10,500
Momci, hocete nesto?

662
00:57:12,250 --> 00:57:13,250
Keks?

663
00:57:29,500 --> 00:57:33,500
Katolicka crkva nije niti
homofobicna niti ignorantna.

664
00:57:34,500 --> 00:57:37,500
Kroz iskljucivanje Boga iz
privatnog zivota,

665
00:57:37,500 --> 00:57:40,500
vlada i sud, slabe vezu
svih kanadana za moralnost.

666
00:57:45,000 --> 00:57:48,000
Oh!... Vidi ovo!

667
00:57:48,000 --> 00:57:51,000
Sad ce te mi jos kazati,
da to nije bolelo?

668
00:58:19,500 --> 00:58:20,500
Gdo. Lorenc...

669
00:58:21,500 --> 00:58:23,500
Je li tacno, da katolici mogu
biti tolerantni prema homoseksualnosti,

670
00:58:23,500 --> 00:58:26,500
dok se isto ne moze reci o
crkvi posebno.

671
00:58:27,750 --> 00:58:28,950
Ustanova, kao sto je.

672
00:58:29,500 --> 00:58:30,500
Je li fer to reci?

673
00:58:30,500 --> 00:58:33,000
Da, mislim, da je to tacno.

674
00:58:33,000 --> 00:58:36,000
Samo dok mislite cinjenje posebno.

675
00:58:37,000 --> 00:58:40,000
Smatrate sebe, kao jedna vise liberarnija
uciteljica vase skole?

676
00:58:41,250 --> 00:58:42,500
Nisam sigurna o tome.

677
00:58:42,500 --> 00:58:45,500
Smatrate onda sebe, kao
liberarna katolitkinja?

678
00:58:46,500 --> 00:58:48,000
Da, da. Mislim da sam.

679
00:58:49,000 --> 00:58:53,000
Vidite, crkvena nauka je cesto otvorena
prema sirokim interpretacijama, koje...

680
00:58:53,000 --> 00:58:54,000
Ali...

